== 观点 ==
王树增认为，若朝鲜再次爆发战争，中国将会采取外交手段，而非直接出兵朝鲜<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://book.sina.com.cn/subject/2009-06-24/1409257214_2.shtml |title=王树增做客新浪读书：中国不会再度出兵朝鲜 |accessdate=2014-11-01 |archive-date=2014-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101174629/http://book.sina.com.cn/subject/2009-06-24/1409257214_2.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

